use you to dwell in this place, in the land that I gave to your fathers, for ever and ever.","year":-610},{"id":"recdyGtVDD4VR0mxt","ref":"Jer.7.8","text":"Behold, ye trust in lying words, that cannot profit.","year":-610}]}
